These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-8-1::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: azure, pink, blue
House: art-deco, futuristic, victorian
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, goat, hedgehog
3 different games are played: monopoly, chess, mah-jongg
City: san-francisco, venice, london
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, aconite, zinnia
 1. the futuristic house is somewhere to the right of the art-deco house##5
 2. the person playing monopoly is not to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##8
 3. the person who likes blue is not to the left of the owner of the goat##8
 4. the owner of the goldfish is the person traveling to london##1
 5. the person traveling to venice is somewhere to the right of the person who growslily##5
 6. the person who growsaconite is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3
 7. the person playing monopoly is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to london##5
 8. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
 9. the futuristic house is somewhere to the left of the person who likes blue##5
10. the person who growsaconite is not to the left of the person playing chess##8
11. the person who growszinnia is on the far left##1
12. the person playing mah-jongg is not to the right of the futuristic house##8
13. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere between the owner of the hedgehog and the person who likes azure##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
| Color          | azure | pink | blue    |
| House           | art-deco | futuristic   | victorian     |
| Pet   | goldfish     | goat   | hedgehog       |
| Game   | chess    | mah-jongg   | monopoly     |
| City   | london    | san-francisco   | venice |
| Flower     | zinnia     | lily | aconite     |

