 3. the person drinking fanta is the bluemaster-smoker##1
 4. the person playing backgammon is not to the left of the person drinking fanta##8
 5. the person who likes pink is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
 6. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
 7. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left##1
 9. the person who likes white is not the oliveros-smoker##6
10. the bluemaster-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##5
11. the person who likes white is not to the right of the person who likes grey##8
12. the person traveling to new-york is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to miami##5
13. the person traveling to miami is somewhere between the person playing billiard and the person who's birthday is in october##7

