The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, poppy, begonia
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, december, april
 1. the polish is not the person who's birthday is in december##6
 2. the turkish is not to the right of the fan of gospel##8
 3. the person who growsiris is somewhere to the right of the prince-smoker##5
 4. the person who growsbegonia is not the person who's birthday is in april##6
 5. the baccarat-smoker is between the fan of house and the person who growspoppy##2
 6. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the turkish##1
 7. the prince-smoker is not to the left of the fan of house##8
 8. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere between the ritmeester-smoker and the fan of house##7
 9. the owner of the guinea-pig is not the baccarat-smoker##6
10. the person who's birthday is in december is between the polish and the person who's birthday is in april##2
11. the turkish is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
12. the fan of d&b is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |        2        |     3     |
| Cigar      | prince       | baccarat         | ritmeester      |
| Music-Genre         | house     | d&b         | gospel    |
| Pet           | guinea-pig  | chinchilla | horse |
| Nationality   | polish    | turkish        | french      |
| Flower         | begonia  | iris        | poppy    |
| Birthday     | november | december      | april      |

